The '''Sixth Decant''' was an area in space near a planetary system where a massive fleet of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyers]] encountered [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] forces in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]]. When the Rebels started falling back and the Imperial commander asked permission to pursue them, [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] personally declined the request, ordering the fleet to stay put.

